title: Adams Carbonless Order Book, 5.56 x 8.44 Inch, 3-Part, Carbonless, 50 Sets, White, Canary, Pink (TC5803)
description: Adams provides the tools to help businesses keep track of messages, finances, transactions, employees, taxes, and customers. Adams Business Forms were designed to help businesses itemize and organize customer information. The Adams Order Book is made from premium grade paper in 3-part sets with a white, canary, pink paper sequence. The sets are carbonless, avoiding the mess of carbon sheets, yet providing extra copies of all orders written to create a permanent record and for distribution to other departments. All sheets contain areas for customer information, order number, terms, and 15 lines for writing order specifics. Each 5.56 x 8.44 inch book contains 50 forms sets with each page consecutively numbered in red, and features a wrap-around cover to prevent write-through. The forms have space at the top for a company stamp to create a professional, customized look. Whether it's a multi-part form, notebooks, writing pads, record books, or any of the hundreds of items we offer, you can count on Adams products to help!
